companyName: Sierra Madre Gold and Silver Ltd.
description: Sierra Madre Gold and Silver Ltd. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of resource properties. It holds an interest in Tepic silver-gold property comprising 5 mining concessions covering an area of 2,615.5 hectares located to the south-southeast from the city of Tepic, Nayarit. The company is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
